Module com.alike
Package com.alike.solvers

Class AntColonyOptimizationSolver

java.lang.Object
com.alike.solvers.AntColonyOptimizationSolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
Solver
public class AntColonyOptimizationSolver extends Object implements Solver
Class uses the Ant colony optimisation algorithm to solve an optimised route through a StaticGraph object.
